ailab (0.0.3) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium

  * Add web management interface (ailab web) with browser-based dashboard,
    live creation/install progress, in-browser terminal, and log tail
  * Add python3-fastapi, python3-uvicorn, python3-aiohttp dependencies
  * Install ailab-web.service systemd user unit for auto-start support
  * Fix lemonade-server detection to check both port 8000 and 13305
  * Add proxy devices for lemonade-server port 13305 (>= 10.1)
  * openclaw: use ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json (openclaw native default path)
  * openclaw: auto-detect lemonade port at install time
  * openclaw: default model Qwen3-4B-Instruct-2507-GGUF; load at install
  * openclaw: run provider setup after onboard so config is not overwritten
  * Suppress spurious chown errors in snap mode
  * Improve postinst messaging; clarify lxd group re-login requirement

